credit.credit-words: We should take it point by point, and let the imagination grasp each scene, especially the closing ones.
"It would be well for us to spend a thoughtful hour each day in contemplation of the life of Christ.
and we shall be more deeply imbued with His spirit."
As we thus dwell upon His great sacrifice for us, our confidence in Him will be more constant, our love will be quickened,
